    "en": {
      "title": "Flight training academy at Batti airport ?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Although Sri Lanka Air Force and the Road Development Authority developed the Batticaloa airport as a local air tours destination in the year 2018, the airport does not generate any revenue at present since it is toll-free of landing and parking charges.",
        "It has been observed that the airport space is suitable to be utilized for other productive purposes considering the above fact.",
        "Accordingly, the Cabinet of Ministers approved the proposal submitted by the Minister of Ports, Naval and Civil Aviation for the invitation of competitive resolutions to establish a flight training academy in the airport of Batticaloa."
      ],
